---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | KOC Cricket" description="Learn about KOC Cricket, how to join, and who runs the club.">
	<section>
		<p class="eyebrow">About us</p>
		<h1>Cricket family on campus</h1>
		<p>
			KOC Cricket is a student-led club focused on building community through weekly practices, league play,
			and campus events. We compete in the Istanbul University League, Bosphorus Cup, and friendly fixtures
			against clubs across Türkiye.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="grid grid--three" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
		<div class="card">
			<h2>Practice times</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Wednesday · 18:00-20:00 · Indoor Training Center</li>
				<li>Saturday · 10:00-12:30 · Kuzey Campus Pitch</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h2>Contacts</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Captain: Ali Kaya · +90 555 123 45 67</li>
				<li>Manager: Elif Demir · elif.demir@ku.edu.tr</li>
				<li>Media: media@koccricket.com</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="card">
			<h2>Community links</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://instagram.com/koccricket" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/koccricket" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/invite/koccricket" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">WhatsApp (players)</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://t.me/koccricket" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Telegram (fans)</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="card" style="margin-top:3rem;">
		<h2>How to contribute</h2>
		<ol>
			<li>Fork or clone the repo.</li>
			<li>Add news, matches, or gallery entries via Decap CMS or Markdown files.</li>
			<li>Submit a PR or push to main to trigger a fresh GitHub Pages deploy.</li>
		</ol>
		<p>
			Questions? Ping us on Instagram or drop an email at koccricket@ku.edu.tr.
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
